         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">26/6/86 ¶ The mail occupies me just much, dear Consul Litton, ¶ Litton was appointed Consul-General for Liberia 'for Australasia and the Islands adjacent thereto' in September 1885 (Victoria,Governmen...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">86.06.26a</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Robert Litton</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">MS 000604, Box 48/f, Geological Society of Australasia correspondence, Royal Historical Society of Victoria, Melbourne.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">26/6/86</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">The mail occupies me just much, dear Consul Litton,</seg>
               <seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Litton was appointed Consul-General for Liberia 'for Australasia and the Islands adjacent thereto' in September 1885 (Victoria,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">Government<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">g</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">azette</seg>, 4 September 1885, p. 2511).</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>and on Tuesday I<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>have to<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>prepare<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>for the great meeting of the geographic Society;</seg>
               <seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>M presided at a meeting of the Victorian Branch of the Geographical Society of Australasia on the evening of Tuesday 29 June 1886, where 'Sir Henry [Governor] and Lady Loch and suite' were in attendance (<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">Age</seg>
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>(Melbourne), 30 June 1886, p. 7).</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>then I will write<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>the<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>notes<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>for<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>the</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>first volume of the geol Soc.;</seg>
               <seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn2" n="3">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>No such notes were ever published.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>but as said before — it is impossible for me, to hold any responsible position for that Society, my time not admitting of attending to its business, as you will see from the delay, which arose, in even furnishing the promised brief notes. So I must adhere to my resolution of relinquishing my position on the Council and the highly honorable post of Vice-President.</seg>
               <seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn3" n="4">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>See M to R. Litton,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>10 June 1886 (in this edition as 86-06-10b).</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>With my best wishes for the welfare of the Society your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Ferd.von Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">I received from the Mines Department a copy of<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>the<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Quaterly<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Report<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn4" n="5">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Quarterly?<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">The gold-f</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">i</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">elds of Victoria: Reports of the mining registrars for the quarter ended<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">31st March<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>1886<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>(?)<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>(Melbourne,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Government Printer),<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>containing Lendenfeld (1886b),<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>an account of the journey of Lendenfeld and Stirling;<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>see M to [R. Litton], January 1886 (in this edition as 86-01-00b).<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
         </div>
      </body>
